        <p class="lead">
          Plumas Disc Golf is a non-profit organization dedicated to furthering
          the sport of disc golf in Plumas County, CA.
        </p>
        <p class="lead">
          PDG was founded by Jeremiah Bridges and Richard Dolezal in 2018. Our
          first course was Pioneer Park Disc Golf Course in Quincy, which was
          made possible by the help of James Shipp of
          <a href="http://cprpd.com/" target="_blank"
            >Central Plumas Recreation and Parks District</a
          >, and we have hopes of opening other courses in the area.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 mr-auto">
        <p class="lead">
          We run tournaments, leagues, fundraisers, and other events to further
          awareness and participation in the sport we love, disc golf. We
          outreach using traditional and social media avenues, including word of
          mouth, flyers, tweets, Facebook posts, and more.
        </p>
      </div>
