          <h3>
            What's your outdoor passion? Winter sports? Snowmobiling? Skiing?
            Mountain biking? Fishing? Camping? Golf? Scenic drives? Relaxation?
            We have it all.
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-0">
            There are lots of Places to Stay all around the county, from
            high-end villas to small motels with friendly local staff. Most
            campgrounds and RV parks are open, so just click on Places to Camp
            to find an ideal spot for you. Plumas County is still virtually
            unknown by many, once you discover the county and visit you will
            return. Plumas County is an easy drive from the Bay Area,
            Sacramento, Reno, and Tahoe. Once here you can sit back and relax or
            choose to challenge yourself, hiking, mountain biking, fishing,
            horseback riding, or off-road adventures. For the motorcyclist we
            have some of the best roads to travel with great scenery. The
            businesses of Plumas County are waiting to serve you and make your
            visit memorable!
